{"tid":1396162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 金融白色恐怖 ]  一人一信 推到 大貓 今日內交代 8月5罷工 立場！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-02T04:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T10:49:43.000Z","uid":286832,"like":75,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"5e9a8021663e59204ee850a8b26c61a7b7b6310f","tid":1396162,"uid":286832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:02:29.000Z","msg":"金融界白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1395174\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1395174</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n入面樓主有相證明自己係員工<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ro03Yba.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fro03Yba.png&h=84d57bd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔理件事係咪真，但大貓無交代過8月5日既安排係事實！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 員工可唔可以調假？！！<br />\n2. 調假/SL 有醫生紙會唔會有處分、秋後算帳？！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下係大貓高層email , 即刻一人一email問下佢地睇法 (email template會再post)<br />\n<br />\nPetertswong@hsbc.com.hk<br />\ndianacesar@hsbc.com.hk<br />\ngreghingston@hsbc.com.hk<br />\nTerence.m.c.chiu@hsbc.com.hk<br />\nBettylam@hsbc.com.hk<br />\nstephanlevieux@hsbc.com.hk<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">另外，除左大貓，<br />\n我地今日要推到依類大集團<br />\n逐間交代員工係咪唔可以行使公民權利表達政治訴求！！！？？？</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要幫手令依d大集團明白：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">////公司存在白色恐怖，<br />\n揚左出去，<br />\n就係一場公關災難////</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">[size=5]要阻止員工罷工，定係阻止一場PR crisis????</span><br />\n<br />\n自己諗la <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ETO1Lff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FETO1Lff.jpg&h=4fff7ac2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25a0084e7fad584fe81455f3b28b080749362ab4","tid":1396162,"uid":286832,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53420b3293dc78583c9ba6c8f802caa32336f4d5","tid":1396162,"uid":286832,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T04:03:03.000Z","msg":"Subject <br />\nPlease ensure the safety of our staff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\nDear Management of HSBC,  <br />\n<br />\nAccording to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress f